--- a/Changes.md
+++ b/Changes.md
@@ -4,6 +4,10 @@ The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/).
 
 ### Unreleased
 
+- fix(transaction): add_header appended to the body instead of the headers #2986
+  - track the end of the header block with found_hb_sep, not header_pos
+  - split headers from body as the data streams in, not in end_data
+  - synthesize a header/body separator when the message arrives without one
 - deps(all): bump versions
 - doc(Plugins): added more sections
 - test: fixes for test-fixtures 1.4 & local plugins that do require('./')
